  "title": "Marketing Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Overview</strong><br />We are looking for a creative and strategic Marketing & Communications Strategist to drive awareness, growth and engagement for our platform. You will work closely with the leadership team to shape our marketing direction, execute campaigns, and manage communications across multiple channels.<br /><br /><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Experience in marketing, communications, or brand strategy.</li><li>Strong writing and storytelling capabilities.</li><li>Comfortable with fast iterations, limited resources and startup pace.</li><li>Familiarity with digital marketing tools (Meta Ads, TikTok, Google Ads, email marketing tools) is a plus.</li><li>Experience working in platform tech, gig economy, transport, or consumer-facing brands is advantageous but not mandatory.</li></ul>",
